This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to summarize student course feedback. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper addresses issues of sparsity, which could place it in cs.CY (Computational Geometry) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
